<tr ><td colspan="3" align="left" valign="top" style="padding-left:35px; padding-right:35px; padding-bottom:25px; " ><div class="mktEditable" id="text2" ><h2 style="text-align: left;">Ovation Select<strong><span style="font-size: 14px;"><sup>TM </sup></span></strong>CS Cabin Management System</h2>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">MHT-to-OST Upgrade for Global Express<span style="vertical-align: baseline; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 20px;"> Aircraft</span></h2>
<h2 style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="color: #191a00; font-size: 12px; line-height: 14.3999996185303px;">Below you will find the link for Honeywell's Sales Bulletin 2015-22:</span></h2>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><a href="https://pages3.honeywell.com/rs/honeywell3/images/2015-22 __Ovation_Select_CS_GEX.pdf">2015-22 __Ovation_Select_CS_GEX.pdf</a></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;">This bulletin describes options that allow operators to mitigate the potential failure of the MHT Galley Touch Screen in their existing Global Express, Ovation C-Series Cabin Management System (CMS) by integrating Ovation Select &trade; digital technology.</p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;"><span style="line-height: 14.3999996185303px;">This bulletin will be sent via e-mail to Honeywell Dealers on Thursday, May 14th, 2015.</span></p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;">Sales Bulletins are also available in the <a href="http://teamsites.honeywell.com/sites/BGAsales/Pages/2015SalesBulletins.aspx">BGA toolkit </a>(Internal Only)</p>
<p style="vertical-align: baseline;">Dealers can find 2015 sales bulletins in the new Honeywell Aerospace Website&nbsp;or in <a href="https://commerce.honeywell.com/webapp/wcs/stores/servlet/HonSalesBulletinView?storeId=10651" target="_blank">MyAerospace</a> under sales bulletins.</p></div>
